Fhenrytangisrubbish%2Fphotos%2Fa.1291135827592566%2F2326812227358249%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=70f704c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/henrytangisrubbish/photos/a.1291135827592566/2326812227358249/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n身兼多重身份的 Joyce Lee，除了創辦 Loey 及 Laboron 外，也是傷心酸辣粉的股東。從小喜歡做生意的她，有著設計時裝的觸覺，成功創立 Laboron 時裝品牌，在上海時裝周更表現出眾。身為設計師兼 CEO 的她，沒有一身華麗的服裝，反而喜歡走型格個性路線。<br />\n<br />\n至於傷心酸辣粉則是後期才成為股東，Joyce主要負責marketing，宣傳及包裝品牌工作，希望提升品牌形象，重新定位，例如加入智能化，重新包裝，令店舖有更舒適的環境。「我才剛開始這邊的工作，希望我的加入能讓這快餐食店的質素提高。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/henrytangisrubbish/photos/a.1291135827592566/2326812227358249/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhenrytangisrubbish%2Fphotos%2Fa.1291135827592566%2F2326812227358249%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=1bd88c11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/henrytangisrubbish/photos/a.1291135827592566/2326812227358249/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://jessicahk.com/articles/shi-ye-xing-nu-xing-de-shi-shang-zhan-yi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjessicahk.com%2Farticles%2Fshi-ye-xing-nu-xing-de-shi-shang-zhan-yi&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=404791d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://jessicahk.com/articles/shi-ye-xing-nu-xing-de-shi-shang-zhan-yi</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hklazybun.gitlab.io/support-hk/boycott/shops/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhklazybun.gitlab.io%2Fsupport-hk%2Fboycott%2Fshops%2F&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=f3ca0e34\" target=\"_blank\">https://hklazybun.gitlab.io/support-hk/boycott/shops/</a>"},{"pid":"0449402b3abf95fb81e96bb0e3fef81604813572","tid":1675873,"uid":162324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a910f8c9b61ce2c163e243785d6602670e8a450","tid":1675873,"uid":107572,"li